Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.10,0:00:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right, everybody!\NKaleido Star is going to start!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star,\Nplease keep your room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.23,0:00:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well. Rosetta here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did everyone watch my trapeze act?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.13,0:00:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was so happy to perform\Nwith Sora, the person I admire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.27,0:00:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to do intense training\Nlike Sora did, and become even better!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm giving the trapeze another\Ntry during my next circus tour,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I've met a certain person there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That person is... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay, let's make a great show\Ntogether again today! Let's! Let's!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:01:02.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss, the beginning\Nis red and black passions{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:09.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometimes, we rely on our contrary hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.60,0:01:16.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss, the last resort is a\Nmission which changes the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.85,0:01:24.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is no place for\Nambiguous answers in love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:32.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even while pretending not to\Nsee the impossible reality, we bet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:38.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hard-to-obtain-truth\NCan you feel me now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:42.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I say to myself,\Nwho gets excited easily?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.31,0:01:46.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm confused about what to say {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:55.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dreamin' the never-waking\Ndream, the falling fate{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:02:02.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't stop lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NYa ya ya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:10.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I believe in you, even\Nif I lose everything for it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:17.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NNo no no{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:23.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's how it is.\NI've gotten the Boss' approval too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to meet my mom,\Nso I'm going on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.48,0:02:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are eight plane tickets. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.44,0:02:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. Uh, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.90,0:02:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's information about\Nthe place we're going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, see you in France!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,France...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,France?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:03:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Leon's Amazing Past."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.44,0:03:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she had her mother,\NMiss Anne, manage it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kenneth's show really lit a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently the condition is that she has to\Ndo diabolo in the show Miss Anne has planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so that's why she left a week early.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the clown team never\Neven dreamed of having this chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this great, Ken?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time I'm only along as your manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't been to France\Nsince the Circus Festival, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time we have to make it\Na France full of smiles, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you people\Ngoing to stand around chatting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get going already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But her words are still sharp...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The taxi stand is this way. Don't dawdle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:04:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I figured it out at that show. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As Sora performs, she watches the audience.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was always just watching Sora or Leon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What Sora has that I was missing\Nis the power to please the audience.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The power to create smiles. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to develop that power, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to first get back my own real smile.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what Miss Layla was trying to teach me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Um... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, {\i1}cirque{\i0}, um, {\i1}noir{\i0}, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oui, mademoiselle. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, great! He seems to understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to split up into two taxis, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, {\i1}cirque{\i0}, um, {\i1}noir{\i0}, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be taking a nap\Nwhen you've got customers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oui! Oui oui oui, mademoiselle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Noir Circus, Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The others should arrive soon too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I wait here until then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you do just a little diabolo performance\Nfor us in the show that starts tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would entail a separate fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were able to contract\Nformer top star Sora Naegino
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Circus Festival winner\NMay Wong at this price
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on the condition that you cast me\Nas a trapeze artist, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I get it, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretend we never had this conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm inexperienced, but I'll do my best\Nnot to disappoint you or the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got high hopes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our star, René.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that was a beautiful move.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're in top form today, René.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alain...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so angry. I'll leave soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've asked you not to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cold, with the\Nrelationship you and I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.81,0:06:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not your pupil anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.90,0:06:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I've sort of run out of cash...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll just buy alcohol\Nwith whatever I give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand well, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For goodness's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I'll be by to pay you back, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.69,0:06:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to repay me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just never show your face in front of me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so generous. So long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alain Rubel. He used to be a\Nfamous trainer of trapeze artists.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trapeze artists?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alain was what you'd call a freelance trainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd scout kids who seemed like\Nthey had a future ahead of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then bring them up to\Nbe first-class trapeze artists.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,René there was one of his students.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually his skill as a\Ntrainer was world-renowned,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he quit doing that several years back,\Nand you've seen what he's become.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A trainer with world-renowned skill...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey, Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Rosetta, from Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach me the trapeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be able to do it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:08:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Kaleido people? You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But doesn't the show start tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\NWe're starting rehearsal right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can follow me,\Nbut it won't do you any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never give up until\Nyou teach me the trapeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place... It's a circus rehearsal space?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now it's only a roomful of junk, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I get on the trapeze?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage is slipping,\Nif they let an amateur like you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make fun of the Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing the trapeze because I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you have such talent...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an interesting girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody told us about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.06,0:09:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\NThis is our main attraction!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3, 2, 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:10:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second, what's with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... This{\i1} is {\i0}the Noir Circus, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Etoile Circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry we're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.23,0:10:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the Kaleido Planets,\Nthe group scheduled to perform today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was going to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but it was interesting! It had thrill.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Noir Circus!\NWe've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry we're late! We're the\Ntouring team from Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Rosetta here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, if you're looking for her\NI think she might be at Alain's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Going to quit already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't quit. Sora never complained\Nabout Leon's special training.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll also...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon? You mean Leon Oswald?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.56,0:11:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's with the Kaleido Stage right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know Leon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I certainly do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was my last pupil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bonjour!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.48,0:11:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, is there anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Leon learned here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:12:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost ten years ago now since\NLeon and his little sister Sophie were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Little sister... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their parents died when they were very\Nyoung and they were taken in by relatives,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but apparently they weren't\Non good terms with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I said I'd like to take them in,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,their adoptive parents agreed right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were brilliant students.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They mastered the basics\Nof the trapeze in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon! Throw Sophie up in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good! Do it over again from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Sophie have enough\Nability to be Leon's partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Or rather,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon didn't have what it\Ntook to be Sophie's partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she was more amazing than Leon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophie might have been able to really do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A perfect Angel's Maneuver...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Angel's Maneuver?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It was my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that in order to make\Nthe Angel's Maneuver a success
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was important for the\Nwoman's partner to become strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I set about training Leon thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.98,0:13:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I'll pick them up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it leaded?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how much I trained Leon,\Nthe Angel's Maneuver just wouldn't gel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was when I started to think that\Nmaybe it was impossible for Leon after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.23,0:13:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophie jacked herself up, as\Nif she were as light as a feather.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw that, I finally understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Angel's Maneuver didn't just\Nrequire the partner to be strong;
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it also required a\Nperformer with an innate instinct
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that sensed the flow of that\Nstrength during performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then if she could just\Nperfectly maintain the pose,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure we could really\Nproduce the Angel's Maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So after that, I trained\NSophie very harshly too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophie! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.98,0:14:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us our money back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophie's been training\Nhard and she's exhausted!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that our problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here to entertain us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being impertinent!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, now we can't pay them their fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the special training.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophie can't withstand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:14:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophie! But you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:15:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you know about "true stars"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"True stars"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The circus troupe we were\Nworking with before told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said the performance of a true star\Nbrings everybody's hearts together as one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling that the Angel's Maneuver\Ncould be a maneuver to become a true star.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon, I want to try doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to perfect the Angel's Maneuver,\Nand try to become a true star.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people who see it, the audience and the\Nother performers, all their hearts will be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they're not related by\Nblood, they'll be just like family...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Angel's Maneuver is a\Nmaneuver to become a true star...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the time I thought\Nshe was talking crazy talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but somewhere along the\Nway even I started thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I wanted to bring\Na true star into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Only a demon can raise an angel."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered hearing that saying\Nfrom a circus troupe I was in long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As we aimed seriously to\Nperfect the Angel's Maneuver
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the special training became\Nmore and more merciless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.10,0:16:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That special training...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as the special\Ntraining I did before the Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophie...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can do a\Nperfect Angel's Maneuver like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say you're going to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing more for us to learn from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll perfect the Angel's Maneuver,\Nand make Sophie a true star.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.06,0:16:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a stepping stone on the way to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:17:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can become a real demon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.69,0:17:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When some years had passed and\NI heard a rumor that Sophie was dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my dream was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.02,0:17:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think Leon had that kind of past...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Leon's special training\Nwas just him trying to break Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it did have a point after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Angel's Maneuver is connected\Nto the path to becoming a true star...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this "true star" thing is a fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to become a star without\Nbeing hated or begrudged by anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.65,0:17:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you have completely\Nperfected the Angel's Maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not so. I think\Ntrue stars can really exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sophie's belief that\Nbeyond the Angel's Maneuver
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lies the path to being a true star...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:17:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please teach me to do\Na perfect Angel's Maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe in such a thing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd just drag you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we'd met at least three years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta, will you keep practicing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, that's the end of\Nboring stories about the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora's eyes are burning more\Nthan I've ever seen them burn before...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've finally found the path to\Nbecoming a true Kaleido Star.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll walk this path! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter how much time it takes,\NI'll become a true Kaleido Star!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it like you've become a part of the trapeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go against the flow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch where the bars will be\Nthree seconds into the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to\Ntell you before you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bars three seconds into the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't relax your efforts now!\NWe're going on to the next stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She came this far in just one day?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cater!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pill-ill-ill-illar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any villain who tries to kill\Nthe princess will have to fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.48,0:19:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why am I the villain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evil queen, say your prayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn the tables on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her move is on a larger scale\Nthan it was in the rehearsal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora's movements are\Ngetting more and more lively.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The last show was like that too,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but this isn't just making the audience smile.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As another performer,\NI'm getting excited too somehow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is Sora's true power... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.27,0:20:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Southern Cross Illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gigashock Explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Infinity Tornado!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fanatic Firestorm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four Thousand Legend Cosmic Dream Spin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's pretty into it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super Beauty Hurricane!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for someone who didn't want to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galactica Unbelievable Splash Thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That girl's performance is\Ndrawing out other people's charm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't let me defeat\Nyou soon, we'll run out of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to, but fine, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that in the script?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's having fun, in her own May way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:21:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget what you've done to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next one, Rosetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.48,0:21:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She did it blindfolded!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.10,0:21:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's just like you, Sora. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You've bounced back from your depression\Nafter the Festival as if it was nothing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.90,0:21:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure that's... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.73,0:21:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, that player named Sora\NNaegino is pretty good, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.19,0:22:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by your physique,\Nyou're a trapeze artist too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.85,0:22:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She certainly does have a strange charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.23,0:22:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might just make that\N"true star" thing a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.19,0:22:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen you somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.65,0:22:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You're Yuri Killian!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.27,0:22:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.73,0:22:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the Kaleido Stage plotting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something big?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.73,0:22:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well now, who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.90,0:22:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've decided on the path\Nthat I'm aiming to walk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.48,0:22:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to master the Angel's Maneuver.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.98,0:22:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I'll do it for sure! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:49.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All kinds of hard luck flocks\Nyour way as if it's spurring you on{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.59,0:22:53.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Swept away by it, time is over {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.72,0:22:56.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as predicted, take it easy {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:23:00.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will get you out right away {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:02.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hurry up (Here we go) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.73,0:23:04.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forcibly only (Drive with the fastest speed){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.57,0:23:08.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The view I look down at every day is the best{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.40,0:23:10.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sunset point (Favorite) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:12.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Harbor light (Stormy night) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.12,0:23:16.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Escape for the sake of tomorrow {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.85,0:23:22.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even I don't have a vacation, I've got an oasis{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.63,0:23:29.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll turn off the cell phone and charge my love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.65,0:23:34.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because some pain,\Nyou can't soothe with just kindness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:38.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are alone, we pass each other by{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:39.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on? {\i0}
